║                         SCRIPT FOR BUYING STOCKS                          ║
╚═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

SCRIPT FOR BUYING STOCKS — is a powerful algorithmic trading software that automates stock purchases based on customizable technical indicators and market conditions. The program connects directly to your brokerage account via API, executes trades automatically, and helps you implement sophisticated investment strategies without manual intervention. Perfect for both beginners and experienced traders looking to systematize their investing.

