    ⚡ HOW THE PROGRAM WORKS:
    ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    
    🔹 CORE ARCHITECTURE
    The program uses a sophisticated algorithmic engine that operates directly from your computer while connecting to brokerage APIs. It functions as a Software-as-a-Service (SaaS) platform that offers automated and algorithmic trading features in a user-friendly interface. Unlike many other platforms that require you to send funds to them, this script does not — instead, it trades from your existing brokerage account using an API (Application Programming Interface) connection .
    
    🔹 BROKERAGE INTEGRATION
    • Direct API connection to major brokerages (TD Ameritrade, E*TRADE, Robinhood, Interactive Brokers)
    • Paper trading mode for risk-free strategy testing with virtual funds
    • Real-time balance and portfolio synchronization
    • Secure encrypted connection — no sensitive data stored locally
    • Support for both cash and margin accounts
    
    🔹 TRADING STRATEGIES
    The script implements multiple proven investment approaches :
    
    • CONTINUOUS BUYING: Performs purchases consistently at each interval, regardless of market price changes. This follows the principle of dollar-cost averaging, allowing users to build an investment position over time.
    
    • DECLINING BUYING: Triggers purchases only when the asset's price has declined from the previous interval's closing price. This approach helps capitalize on lower price points, potentially improving average costs during downward trends.
    
    • MOMENTUM STRATEGY: Buys stocks showing strong upward price movement with high relative strength
    
    • MEAN REVERSION: Identifies oversold conditions using RSI and Bollinger Bands for bounce opportunities
    
    • MOVING AVERAGE CROSSOVER: Generates buy signals when short-term MA crosses above long-term MA 
    
    🔹 ENTRY CONDITIONS
    Users can configure sophisticated entry rules combining multiple technical indicators :
    
    • PRICE-BASED: Buy when price crosses above/below specific moving averages (SMA 20/50/200)
    • INDICATOR-BASED: RSI thresholds (oversold/overbought), MACD crossovers, Bollinger Band touches
    • VOLUME-BASED: Entry on unusual volume spikes or volume confirmations
    • FUNDAMENTAL FILTERS: P/E ratio, earnings growth, sector performance
    • COMBINATION RULES: Support for multiple 'and'/'or' conditions between indicators
    
    🔹 DYNAMIC INVESTMENT ADJUSTMENT
    Advanced feature that increases purchasing amount when prices decline :
    
    • If enabled, increases buying amount by 50% when current price falls by user-defined percentage
    • Helps accumulate larger positions during market dips
    • Improves long-term cost averaging
    • Configurable threshold and multiplier settings
    
    🔹 EXIT CONDITIONS
    Multiple methods to close positions and secure profits :
    
    • TAKE PROFIT: Automatically sell when price reaches target percentage gain
    • STOP LOSS: Limit losses with automatic sell at defined loss threshold
    • TRAILING STOP: Dynamic stop that follows price upward
    • TECHNICAL EXIT: Sell based on indicator signals (RSI overbought, MA death cross)
    • TIME-BASED: Auto-close positions at end of trading day (for day trading)
    
    🔹 BACKTESTING ENGINE
    Test your strategies against historical data before risking real money :
    
    • Custom time windows: 1D, 1W, 1M, 3M, 1Y, or custom date ranges
    • Performance metrics: Win rate, profit factor, max drawdown, Sharpe ratio
    • Visual charts showing entry/exit points on price history
    • Comparison mode: Test multiple strategies side-by-side
    • Export results to CSV/PDF for detailed analysis
    • Note: Past performance does not guarantee future results
    
    🔹 AI-POWERED SIGNALS (Premium Feature)
    Advanced machine learning integration for smarter trading decisions :
    
    • Analyzes information from over 3,000 data sources including sentiment data
    • Processes large volumes of market data for AI modeling with substantial computational resources
    • Generates buy/watch/sell recommendations with confidence scores
    • Provides fundamental quality scores (1-10) for each stock
    • Includes investment thesis, pros/cons, and risk assessment
    
    🔹 MARKET INTELLIGENCE
    Enhanced stock selection tools :
    
    • ADR% (Average Daily Range): Measures stock volatility using 20-day average percentage move
    • INTRINSIC INTELLIGENCE: Aggregates insights from 3,000+ data sources
    • SENTIMENT ANALYSIS: Tracks social media, news, and analyst sentiment
    • VOLATILITY METRICS: Real-time volatility calculations
    • LIQUIDITY SCREENING: Filter stocks by average daily volume and market cap
    
    🔹 AUTOMATION FEATURES
    • 24/7 market monitoring across global exchanges
    • Scheduled scanning at custom intervals (1min to daily)
    • Instant execution when conditions are met
    • Multi-stock portfolio management
    • Up to 10 concurrent strategies running simultaneously 
    
    🔹 RISK MANAGEMENT
    • Position sizing calculator based on portfolio risk percentage
    • Maximum allocation limits per stock/strategy
    • Daily loss limits to prevent over-trading
    • Diversification rules to avoid concentration
    • Emergency stop-all button to halt all trading
